{"tid":1815392,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[學術討論] N95口罩 VS 普通外科口罩","createTime":"2020-01-07T12:57:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T12:35:43.000Z","uid":49471,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0034c107c89c3f6506179ff8a171b85a63f24a5f","tid":1815392,"uid":49471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:57:42.000Z","msg":"呢幾日好多口罩post，我試下歸納咁多位巴打同埋3M針對H1N1肺炎出既專業Report（link：<br />\n<a href=\"http://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/604799O/ohes-h1n1-influenza-a-faq.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmultimedia.3m.com%2Fmws%2Fmedia%2F604799O%2Fohes-h1n1-influenza-a-faq.pdf&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=1204107e\" target=\"_blank\">http://multimedia.3m.com/mws/media/604799O/ohes-h1n1-influenza-a-faq.pdf</a>)<br />\n<br />\nQ1. 外科口罩比N95更好？N95冇做fitting test同唔戴冇分別？<br />\n<br />\nA1：一般醫學外科口罩其實冇咁安全，因為肺炎呢一類疾病可以經過空氣傳播。普通醫學口罩係設計用於防止液體同埋血液飛濺，並唔有效阻礙空氣粒子傳播。所以就算你唔係前線醫護人員，一般市民用N95會比醫學口罩更有效預防肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n但係的確，現階段唔知呢隻中國肺炎咩料，冇人知平時出街需唔需要用到N95，普通外科口罩會比較平同埋會戴得舒服d，所以出街用邊隻口罩取決於你有幾謹慎。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ2. 唔做fitting test戴N95，不如戴返外科口罩？<br />\n<br />\nA2. 空氣密封測試的確重要，但跟說明書做，自己都test到。如果講漏氣，點都係外科口罩嚴重d。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ3. N95口罩係咪一定要用醫療果隻，工業用果隻唔岩用？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1WR5P7N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1WR5P7N.png&h=2c2df06c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nA3. 其實唔係喺手術室或者前線環境 (有機會接觸到血液同埋體液)，根本唔需要用到醫療N95/ FDA certified。一般市民係可以佩戴工業用N95 i.e. 3M 8210/8210v/8155/9010/9010v<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ4. V版本有氣閥（Valved）既N95口罩隔唔隔到病菌？<br />\n<br />\nA4. 隔離post見到有巴打話V版口罩有氣閥既N95冇用，真係好大既誤會。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NUgxu7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNUgxu7C.jpg&h=2e308233&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5kXs3sY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5kXs3sY.jpg&h=cec5cd3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個氣閥係3M專利，令呼吸暢順舒服好多，有出冇入，適合冇病嘅人。但如果你係確診病人就唔應該用，因為病菌可以由valve呼出。<br />\n<br />\nEg 3M 8210v / 9010V / 8155"},{"pid":"c486d2bc0f7772c3594b7daf03b4f9b333989a10","tid":1815392,"uid":49471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"有請其他巴打補充/指正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9902b304a805c85b220e73a4bd2f0e3259cc5c72","tid":1815392,"uid":181581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"豬嘴係咪可以拎返出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fb137026b150606d474c4c2af4a942d425ec54","tid":1815392,"uid":303528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:07:47.000Z","msg":"認真post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa33598603391818b11643728d18feac8a807284","tid":1815392,"uid":49471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9902b304a805c85b220e73a4bd2f0e3259cc5c72","tid":1815392,"uid":181581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"豬嘴係咪可以拎返出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"好似唔係用黎防疫wor巴打"},{"pid":"7e0709a39421e34cf07f3327965c9d56fd454fbd","tid":1815392,"uid":238369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aa33598603391818b11643728d18feac8a807284","tid":1815392,"uid":49471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9902b304a805c85b220e73a4bd2f0e3259cc5c72","tid":1815392,"uid":181581,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:01:52.000Z","msg":"豬嘴係咪可以拎返出嚟用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:08:15.000Z","msg":"好似唔係用黎防疫wor巴打"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:11:21.000Z","msg":"如果催淚煙啲有機氣體微粒都阻隔到<br />\n<br />\n你覺得飛沬會阻隔唔到咩？"},{"pid":"ac0d80a056b42b5f42746ca1b2dd65bc1a6c68ab","tid":1815392,"uid":49471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:32:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa95a04300e80fc76a5e03a07afbbdffe8ae7373","tid":1815392,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"1860/1870先防菌咩唔係<br />\n呢啲防粉塵喎"},{"pid":"b70bc1fb872e41a83e303b91bc66afbe4770fe21","tid":1815392,"uid":92426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:43:37.000Z","msg":"呢篇文指其實 surgical mask 封 PM2.5 效果其實唔錯:<br />\n<a href=\"https://smartairfilters.com/en/blog/surgical-masks-surprisingly-effective-pm2-5/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsmartairfilters.com%2Fen%2Fblog%2Fsurgical-masks-surprisingly-effective-pm2-5%2F&d=rLp99s1CaA%2FTm5LA4NL6TfRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=a976fa7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://smartairfilters.com/en/blog/surgical-masks-surprisingly-effective-pm2-5/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外科口罩防唔到virus,  但防水(飛沫) + 細菌, 其實都好夠做. 重點係平, 可以日日帶.<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>普通醫學口罩係設計用於防止液體同埋血液飛濺，並唔有效阻礙空氣粒子傳播。</blockquote><br />\n重點都係要睇傳播途徑係 氣沬 定 &quot;空氣粒子&quot; ."},{"pid":"d3fa213891ea391b2bf83813b94d92657651b78f","tid":1815392,"uid":69157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa95a04300e80fc76a5e03a07afbbdffe8ae7373","tid":1815392,"uid":69157,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:34:03.000Z","msg":"1860/1870先防菌咩唔係<br />\n呢啲防粉塵喎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T13:44:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qXNkEf2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqXNkEf2.png&h=366f1fb1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e52a390be9a5d8ab37eb1ea6c726e4471dba8e92","tid":1815392,"uid":207792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7e0709a39421e34cf07f3327965c9d56fd454fbd","tid":1815392,"uid":238369,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aa33598603391818b11643728d18feac8a807284","tid":1815392,"uid":49471,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"